cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper introduces a modular aerial robotic platform and proposes an IMU-based estimation strategy for flight control. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper discusses the development of flight modules and a control module for the system. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a possibility as the paper mentions trajectory tracking flights, which may involve computer vision techniques. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper mentions an adaptive geometric controller for refinement of uncertain parameters. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper discusses the use of an IMU-based estimation strategy and an adaptive scheme for stable flights.
